getMapKeyForTradingProperty

protected java.lang.Object getMapKeyForTradingProperty(TradingProperty tradingProperty)
This method is used to get an Object to be used as the key for adding, obtaining and removing the TradingProperty's from the underlying Map collection returned from getTradingPropertyMap(). This implementation always returns an Integer object representing the auction type. This enforces the cardinality of only one existing per auction type.

Overrides:
getMapKeyForTradingProperty in class AbstractTradingPropertyGroup
Parameters:

Returns:
